          ::
          ++  sub-safe
            |=  [a=@ b=@]
            ^-  @
            ?:((lte a b) 0 (sub a b))
          ::  +show: produce a printable version of .metrics
          ::
          ++  show
            =/  ms  (div ~s1 1.000)
            ::
            :*  rto=(div rto ms)
                rtt=(div rtt ms)
                rttvar=(div rttvar ms)
